---
title: Smart Bacon and Egg Spinach Salad with Warm Bacon Vinaigrette, Potatoes and Mushrooms
description: Nothing takes a salad to new levels of luxury quite like a warm shallot and bacon vinaigrette! You'll want to coat every bite of salad in its sweet-savoury-tangy flavour.

